aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ecp1665702743903.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ecp1665702743903.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ecp1665702743903.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ecp1665702743903\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Section of the <span class=\"ph filepath\">web.xml</span> file containing the definition and settings for the SOAP Request Dispatcher (SRD).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ecp1665702743903__section_N1001D_N1001A_N10001\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d850212e53\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ecp1665702743903__p_d147287e1_d147288e1_d147289e1\">Uniface servlets run in the environment of the Web Application; the the SOAP Request Dispatcher (SRD) definition and settings are stored in the SRD servlet configuration section in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">web.xml</span> file, which is the configuration file of the Web Application (not to be confused with the Uniface WebApplication Server).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ecp1665702743903__p_d147290e1_d147291e1_d147292e1\">The SRD servlet configuration section uses the following format:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;web-app&gt;\n&lt;!-- Uniface S(oap) R(equest) D(ispatcher) Servlet --&gt;\n&lt;servlet&gt;\n &lt;servlet-name&gt;srd&lt;/servlet-name&gt;\n &lt;servlet-class&gt;com.rocketsoftware.uniface.urd.SRDServlet&lt;/servlet-class&gt; \n &lt;init-param&gt;\n &lt;param-name&gt;<var class=\"keyword varname\">ParamName</var>&lt;/param-name&gt;\n &lt;param-value&gt;<var class=\"keyword varname\">ParamValue</var>&lt;/param-value&gt;\n &lt;/init-param&gt;\n&lt;!-- More servlet settings... --&gt;\n&lt;/servlet&gt;\n&lt;!-- More servlet definitions --&gt;\n&lt;/web-app&gt;\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ecp1665702743903__p_d147293e1_d147294e1_d147295e1\">where</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ecp1665702743903__li_d51158e1_d51159e1_d51160e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ParamName</var>—name of the SRD servlet setting, for example <code class=\"ph codeph\">MIDDLEWARE</code>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ecp1665702743903__li_d51161e1_d51162e1_d51163e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ParamValue</var>—value of the SRD servlet setting.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xvg1665702743974.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Configuration Settings: Uniface Servlet</a><p>Uniface servlets run in the environment of the web application. Settings for the Uniface servlets, the WRD and SRD, are stored in the web.xml file, which is the configuration file of the web application.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527073\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527073\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "SRD Servlet Section Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Section of the web.xml file containing the definition and settings for the SOAP Request Dispatcher (SRD). Description Uniface servlets run in the environment of the Web Application; the the SOAP Request Dispatcher (SRD) definition and settings are stored in the SRD servlet configuration section in the web.xml file, which is the configuration file of the Web Application (not to be confused with the Uniface WebApplication Server). The SRD servlet configuration section uses the following format: <web-app> <!-- Uniface S(oap) R(equest) D(ispatcher) Servlet --> <servlet> <servlet-name>srd</servlet-name> <servlet-class>com.rocketsoftware.uniface.urd.SRDServlet</servlet-class> <init-param> <param-name> ParamName </param-name> <param-value> ParamValue </param-value> </init-param> <!-- More servlet settings... --> </servlet> <!-- More servlet definitions --> </web-app> Copy where ParamName —name of the SRD servlet setting, for example MIDDLEWARE . ParamValue —value of the SRD servlet setting. Related Links Configuration Settings: Uniface Servlet Uniface servlets run in the environment of the web application. Settings for the Uniface servlets, the WRD and SRD, are stored in the web.xml file, which is the configuration file of the web application. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}